self.pm provides $self and @args for your Perl OO modules, so you don't need to
say:

    my $self = shift;

And this is no source filter.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

None.


